Hackathons.title: Hackathons
Hackathons.tagline: Do you want to organize a hackathon for your school, club, or community? We will help you plan the event, manage budgeting, bring in mentors, and invite prestigous judges.

Speaking Engagements.title: Speaking Engagements
Speaking Engagements.tagline: Would you like a guest speaker to talk about the future of education, technology, business strategy? Our speakers will be available for press before & after the event to spend time with the audience, answer Q&A, and we will help you promote the event.

Workshops.title: Workshops
Workshops.tagline: Host a workshop for your school, club, business and offer your members the opportunity to learn about responsive web development, React app development, Unity game development, and more.
